this is my first socket project!!
its a mini chat app to run this program you have to:


-- make java project chat
-- create chat package inside src
-- out the 3 files inside the chat package
-- compile all : in cmd use 
javac src/chat/*.java

-- run Serveur first: in cmd use 
java -cp src chat.Serveur

-- run multiple Clients instance : in cmd use 
java -cp src chat.Client

...and thats it! hope you enjoy my Nchatapp
